titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: HYPOXIC ISCHEMIC ENCEPHALOPATHY GRADE (HIGHEST ON NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE) - Description

div.p: HYPOXIC ISCHEMIC ENCEPHALOPATHY GRADE (HIGHEST ON NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE) is the highest HYPOXIC ISCHEMIC ENCEPHALOPATHY GRADE recorded on the NEONATAL CRITICAL CARE DAILY CARE DATE.
